               <n2016:NUTS CODE="UK"/>
               <MAIN_SITE>
                  <P>London SW1P 4DR.</P>
               </MAIN_SITE>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>It is proposed that Lot 2 of STAR Two would feature a new Category F comprising of up to 6 suppliers each capable of providing highly strategic commercial advice for transport. Lot 2 is intended to be used for occasional short term consultancy commissions.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <INFO_ADD>
                  <P>This notice is for information. A Separate Contract Notice containing further details is expected to be issued shortly to start the formal pre-qualification process.</P>
               </INFO_ADD>
            </OBJECT_DESCR>
