            <INFO_ADD>
               <P>It is intended that the STARTwo framework will be procured under PCR 2015 using a 2 stage restricted procedure.</P>
               <P>This notice is for information. A separate contract notice containing further details is expected to be issued at the end of April to start the formal pre-qualification process.</P>
               <P>A short briefing pack setting out an overview of the authority’s current proposals, the indicative timeline for the procurement completion and details of how to register your interest in attending a ticket only STARTwo engagement event, is available from the STAR framework team. To receive a copy interested parties are invited to email the following address: STAR-Framework@dft.gsi.gov.uk</P>
